        <mxCell id="migration" value="Required App Changes Before Internal Go-Live&#xa;1. SQLite -&gt; PostgreSQL&#xa;2. Local uploads folder -&gt; Blob/ADLS&#xa;3. Hardcoded localhost API -&gt; env config&#xa;4. Open CORS -&gt; allow Volvo internal origin only&#xa;5. Add Entra ID auth and role checks" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#fff2cc;strokeColor=#d6b656;fontSize=14;" vertex="1" parent="1">
